1
00:00:01,744 --> 00:00:02,994
Guru Mahārāj says,

2
00:00:02,994 --> 00:00:06,734
“Subjective evolution
parallels objective evolution.”

3
00:00:08,324 --> 00:00:12,594
Meaning, and it’s similar to

4
00:00:13,658 --> 00:00:17,447
sāṅkhya as described 
in the Third Canto of Śrīmad Bhāgavatam,

5
00:00:17,447 --> 00:00:19,307
there is Kapila’s sāṅkhya,

6
00:00:19,307 --> 00:00:22,527
the theist Kapila, 
[and] the atheist Kapila.

7
00:00:22,527 --> 00:00:28,213
They’re both analyzing life, the elements,
the Universe—all these things.

8
00:00:28,292 --> 00:00:30,890
[Soul Driven Evolution]

9
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:33,957
But we’re told sometimes, 
“What’s the difference?”

10
00:00:33,957 --> 00:00:37,188
One—twenty four divisions 
of twenty five,

11
00:00:37,188 --> 00:00:40,838
what’s the twenty fifths?
The soul, ātma.

12
00:00:40,838 --> 00:00:45,448
That the soul is what’s driving
all of this.

13
00:00:45,448 --> 00:00:50,440
So the soul is driving 
objective evolution.

14
00:00:51,135 --> 00:00:55,404
So we can say, in the subjective
evolution of consciousness

15
00:00:55,404 --> 00:00:59,444
that the soul is evolving 
from lowest species,

16
00:00:59,444 --> 00:01:03,144
finished with that body,
terms of karmic imprisonment,

17
00:01:03,144 --> 00:01:06,208
punishment, reaction …

18
00:01:11,178 --> 00:01:12,352
to say …

19
00:01:14,262 --> 00:01:18,348
expressing the reactions 
of karmic activity,

20
00:01:18,908 --> 00:01:24,208
but another word meaning 
to finish with them …

21
00:01:24,412 --> 00:01:27,097
Anyway, so the soul evolving 
 

22
00:01:27,097 --> 00:01:29,447
jala-jā nava-lakṣāṇi sthāvarā 
[Viṣṇu Purāṇa]

23
00:01:29,447 --> 00:01:35,321
from aquatics to plants,
to insects, birds, beasts,

24
00:01:35,321 --> 00:01:38,321
at last to the human species.

25
00:01:38,321 --> 00:01:41,948
So, some interpreters are saying,
“The athāto—

26
00:01:41,948 --> 00:01:45,624
now, that you’ve achieved
human life,

27
00:01:45,624 --> 00:01:48,254
now that you can understand 
what I am saying,

28
00:01:48,254 --> 00:01:52,136
now that you can hear

29
00:01:52,136 --> 00:01:55,926
what I am trying
to convey to you,

30
00:01:55,926 --> 00:02:01,557
now that you can conceive 
such things properly,

31
00:02:01,557 --> 00:02:05,553
now that you’re 
conscience being

32
00:02:05,553 --> 00:02:08,553
whose not only aware 
of your existence,

33
00:02:08,553 --> 00:02:11,713
but of а particular inner
necessity you have.”

